From 4d91714dd33234988866b2e238effb632a2b8b87 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Mar 2026 17:34:58 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 54/66] Remove dead XPC code from Chromium

The XPC gateway whispered goodbye,
As sockets took over the sky.
StartDynamicMode fell,
CloseTab rang its bell,
And HandleQueryTabs waved from on high.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
